        <mxCell id="scorer-info1" parent="o4QgxmDZ_h19-OYWXaL5-9" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontStyle=0" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;qualityScorer (Haiku Judge)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Pipeline: analyze(&lt;font color=&quot;#E65100&quot;&gt;LLM&lt;/font&gt;) → generateScore(code) → generateReason(code)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Relevance (0.35)&lt;/b&gt;: 응답이 질문에 실제로 답하는가&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Completeness (0.30)&lt;/b&gt;: 질문의 모든 측면을 다루는가&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Usefulness (0.20)&lt;/b&gt;: 실질적 정보 vs &quot;결과 없음&quot;&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Coherence (0.15)&lt;/b&gt;: 구조, 가독성, 논리적 조직화&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;quality-check Step 2단계에서 의미 기반 평가&lt;br&gt;+ &lt;font color=&quot;#E65100&quot;&gt;improvementSuggestion&lt;/font&gt; → Classifier에 개선 방향 전달&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="180" width="340" x="1775" y="415" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
